description:
In the middle of the HafenCity you will find the Business Center in the modern and extraordinary Sumatrakontor. HafenCity is one of the most spectacular new building projects in Europe, where you will find the Elbphilharmonie Concert Hall, among others.
Rental prices and equipment
This business center has 10-50 sqm of offices, which can be equipped according to your wishes. The rental price depends on the size of the office, regardless of whether you use it as an individual or team office. In addition to the furnished office, additional costs such as WIFI, cleaning and mail service are already included in the rental price. The public areas, such as the kitchen, are shared and are included. You also have the possibility to book conference rooms flexibly if required.
Location and accessibilityThe office property is located in the middle of HafenCity, which on the one hand offers the typical maritime flair and on the other hand is characterised by the development of this part of town through new buildings. Due to its proximity to the city center, which is within walking distance, this location offers you a variety of shopping opportunities. Also in the immediate vicinity you will find numerous shopping and gastronomic offers. The connection is guaranteed by the underground Überseequartier, which is only a few minutes' walk from the office. In addition, the location allows for a quick connection to the A1, which is only a few minutes' drive away.

The Business Center is located in an excellent location in Berlin's inner city and convinces with its appealing building architecture. The renovated office and conference rooms offer a pleasant working environment. The underground station "Französische Straße" is only a few meters away. In the immediate vicinity you can find various shopping possibilities as well as a variety of gastronomic offers. Parking spaces can be rented in the in-house underground car park.

The Business Center is located in the immediate vicinity of Berlin's main railway station, which offers excellent transport connections to local and long-distance public transport. The government quarter with the Chancellery, the Ministry of the Interior and the Reichstag building is within walking distance.
The building is a value-stable and representative new building and convinces by its environmentally conscious and sustainable construction method. The elevators and the ABC Center can be reached via a spacious reception hall. The rooms there are equipped to the latest standards. All offices and conference rooms have large windows and high ceilings, which make the rooms bright and spacious. A restaurant on the ground floor with a terrace overlooking the park is being planned. Sufficient parking spaces are available in the building.

The ABC Business Center is located in the immediate vicinity of Frankfurt's main railway station and thus offers a central location. The building has office space, private offices and stylish conference rooms. Thanks to the renovation work carried out in 2018, the offices meet the latest standards and offer you the perfect workplace. Rental PricesThe office space offers space for more than 20 employees and is already fully equipped. You can rent office space here on short or long-term basis at flexible conditions. Our team will be happy to assist you in finding the optimal composition of your office space so that you can concentrate on your work. EquipmentThe modernly equipped offices and conference rooms are located on the 3rd and 5th floors and are considered as new. Due to the corner location of the offices, they have plenty of daylight and thus offer a pleasant working environment with a breathtaking view. The 1GBit fast business fibre optic internet connection provides you with an optimal connection. Location and accessibilityThe ABC Business Center is located opposite the Westend-Tower directly in the banking district of Frankfurt, between the Alte Oper and the Platz der Republik and is easily accessible by bicycle and public transport. The building is only a few minutes' walk from Frankfurt's main railway station. The surrounding multi-storey car parks also offer sufficient parking facilities within a short distance. Are you looking for an office or flexible office space in modern and luxurious style in the centre of Frankfurt? Please contact us for a viewing of this business center in Frankfurt.

The Business Center is located not far from Hamburg Airport and offers you individual and team offices that you can rent flexibly according to your needs. The highlight of the property is the roof terrace, which you can share. There is also a Holiday Shuttle that takes you to the airport every 10 minutes free of charge.

Rental prices/equipmentThe fully furnished offices are 10-50 sqm in size and all have WLAN. The public areas such as the lounge can be used by all office users. Included services include utilities, WIFI, cleaning and a mail service. The rooms can be furnished individually according to your wishes. You book the office and determine the number of workstations yourself. In addition to the offices, you will find conference rooms that you can book as required and which are also equipped to a high standard.

Location and accessibilityYou will find the Business Center in the Obenhauptstraße not far from the airport. You can also reach the A7 motorway in only 10 minutes by car. The city centre can be reached in 20 minutes by car. You have a connection to the public transport via the bus stop which is only a few meters from the object.

The Business Center, which is located in a modernized building in the middle of Hamburg's city center, has spacious offices that can be flexibly designed and rented.

Rental prices and equipmentThe offices have 10-50 sqm and can be furnished individually according to your wishes. You do not pay for the individual workstations here, but for the fully equipped office. You decide the number of workstations yourself. The costs for an office vary according to size, all services such as utilities, WIFI, office equipment and postal service are also included in the price. If you need a conference room, you can book one flexibly.

Location and accessibilityThe ABC Business Center is located in the heart of Hamburg city centre, just a few minutes' walk from Hamburg's main railway station. The well-known shopping streets Mönckebergstraße and Spitalerstraße are also not far from the location. The Binnenalster and Jungfernstieg are also within easy reach. Via the main station you have a connection to the entire Hamburg public transport system as well as to the long-distance traffic. In addition, the location allows for a quick connection to the A1, which is only a few minutes' drive away.

The 14-storey office building is located on the Alster. Here you can expect spacious offices in a prime location. The offices are flooded with light through the large window fronts and are equipped with electric external sun protection and cooling ceilings, which ensure a pleasant temperature even on summer days.

Rental prices and equipmentThe flexible rentable offices have 10-50 sqm and are individually equipped according to your wishes. All necessary workstations are made available to you. The price refers to the size of the office, regardless of how many workstations you wish to integrate. All additional costs such as WIFI, office equipment and mail service are also included in the price.

Location and accessibilityThe site is located between the Binnen- and Außenalster on the Esplanade in Hamburg city centre. Next to the Alster you will also find Planten un Bloomen within walking distance, where you can take a nice lunchtime walk. The central location is characterized by a variety of supply possibilities, which leave nothing to be desired. The underground station Stephansplatz is only a few minutes' walk away. The central station and the Dammtor station are also close to the property, which gives you access to long-distance transport. In addition, the location allows for a quick connection to the A1, which is only a few minutes' drive away.

The Agendis Business Center is located in a 16-story office building in the west of Frankfurt, close to the Frankfurt trade fair. The building has modern office space, private offices and comfortable conference rooms.Rental pricesThe office spaces offer a lot of space and are already fully equipped. You can rent office space here on short or long-term basis at flexible conditions. Our team will be happy to assist you in finding the optimum combination of office space so that you can concentrate on your work.EquipmentThe high-quality equipped offices and conference rooms offer a professional atmosphere. Due to the glass façade, the offices have plenty of daylight and thus offer a pleasant working environment with a breathtaking view. The modern access control system and the in-house security service guarantee a high level of security.Location and accessibilityThe Agendis Business Center is centrally located on one of the most important access roads in Frankfurt, between the city center and the airport, and close to the Frankfurt Trade Fair and the banking district. The surrounding area offers an optimal infrastructure as well as connections to the main railway station and public transport. The company's own underground car park offers sufficient parking space. Are you looking for an office or flexible office space in modern and luxurious style in the centre of Frankfurt? Please contact us for a viewing of this business center in Frankfurt.

Whether a small individual office, team office or an entire office floor, this building leaves nothing to be desired. The Business Center in the Radlkoferstrasse in Munich impresses with its representative office building with its fascinating natural stone façade. Large windows provide for excellently lit interior and office spaces. The office centre offers a personalised room layout and size of office space, which can be rented under flexible contractual conditions. There are 45 fully equipped offices ranging in size from 12 to 30 square metres. The reception area, conference room, kitchenette, sanitary facilities and lounge are shared and, like your office, are cleaned daily. A total of 11,000 square metres of office space is distributed over 5 floors with separate entrances and two lifts.
 
Rental prices and equipment
The furnished offices can be rented very flexibly, which means that you do not take any risk. You can flexibly rent additional offices or terminate the lease agreement for unused office space. The prices can vary depending on the rental period. Not only are you open 24 hours a day, but you can also enjoy other services such as an installed telephone system, secretarial services, reception services, IT services, air conditioning, photocopiers and daily cleaning as well as the use of the tea/coffee kitchen included in the rent. This way you can concentrate fully on your work and the local service staff will take care of the rest.
 
Location and accessibility
The modern business centre is located in the friendly surroundings of Radlkoferstrasse in the district of Sendlingen and thus in the centre of Munich. Via the Mittlerer Ring you can reach all motorways in Munich quickly and easily. By public transport you can reach the main station, Marienplatz or the English Garden in only 5 minutes. Also the Theresienwiese is only 200 meters away, where you will find a wide range of restaurants and bars, which invite you to have lunch or dinner.

Auf dem Gelände des alten Flughafen München Riem ist die denkmalgeschützte Wappenhalle Blickfang und Zentrum. Zehn eigenständige, moderne Bürogebäude umgeben heute den Komplex und machen die Immobilie sicher zu einem der individuellsten Gewerbeobjekte, die derzeit am Gelände der Neuen Messe München stehen. Zu den augenblicklichen Mietern gehören unter anderem Brainlab AG, Hochschule der bayerischen Wirtschaft (HDBW), Symantec (Deutschland) GmbH.
Von Büroräumen ab 14 m² stehen Ihnen hier verschiedenste Räume und Flächen bis hin zur abgeschlossenen Büroetage zur Verfügung – 100 komplett ausgestattete Einzel- und Großraumbüros, flexibel ausgestattet und nutzbar je nach der Anzahl der benötigten Arbeitsplätze.
Die Benutzung der hochwertigen Infrastruktur des Gebäudes, wie z. B. Empfang und Loungebereiche, Konferenzräume, Teeküchen etc. ist bei Anmietung eines Büros inklusive.

The Agendis Business Center Frankfurt North is located in a central area of the popular Merton quarter. The building has office space, private offices as well as conference, meeting and training rooms. The offices meet the latest standards and offer you the perfect workplace.Rental PricesThe office spaces offer a lot of space and are already fully equipped. You can rent office space here on short or long-term basis at flexible conditions. Our team will be happy to assist you in finding the optimum combination of office space so that you can concentrate on your work.EquipmentThe modernly equipped offices and conference rooms have plenty of natural light and thus offer a pleasant working environment with a breathtaking view. The fast business fibre optic internet connection provides you with an optimal connection.Location and accessibilityThe Agendis Business Center Frankfurt North is centrally located in the popular Merton quarter. The four-storey office building is located just a few kilometres north of Frankfurt city centre, in the immediate vicinity of one of the most important transport links and within walking distance of the nearest underground station. Are you looking for an office or flexible office space in a modern style in Frankfurt? Please contact us for a viewing of this business center in Frankfurt.

The Business Center is located in Leopoldstraße in picturesque Schwabing in Munich in a quiet environment. The modern office building is designed with high-quality exterior walls made of glass and bricks. It is a U-shaped unit consisting of two main buildings and a connected building. Thanks to the large glass surface, the office building offers you friendly rooms full of light, which you can rent for a minimum of 1 month.
The office centre in the famous Leopoldstraße offers you fully furnished offices with a surface area of approx. 12 to 65 square metres. IT cables and high-speed fibre optic cables have been installed in the offices to meet the highest office requirements. The conference room for up to 40 people is optional and can be rented flexibly. A multilingual assistant will be happy to answer your questions or to welcome your customers. There are also sufficient parking spaces in the in-house underground car park.
 
Rental prices and equipment
The furnished offices can be rented in a very flexible way, which means that you do not take any risk and you also have the possibility to rent additional offices or to cancel the rental contract for unused office space. The price can vary depending on the rental period. In addition to round-the-clock access, the rental price includes other amenities such as pre-installed telephone systems, secretarial service, reception service, IT service, air conditioning, photocopiers, daily cleaning and use of the tea/coffee kitchen. This allows you to concentrate fully on your work and the service personnel on site will take care of the rest.
 
Location and accessibility
The office centre borders on the one hand on the Munich television tower and on the other on the Olympic Park. It is located in Leopoldstraße with an optimal connection to the road network and public transport in Munich. Many shops, bars, restaurants and hotels are within walking distance, thus ensuring that you can enjoy your lunch break. Public transport is only a few minutes away, from where you can reach all important places in the city.

The Agendis Business Center is located in a new business area in the immediate vicinity of Frankfurt Airport.Rental PricesYou can rent the office space for short or long periods at flexible conditions. Our team will be happy to assist you in finding the optimal composition of your office space so that you can concentrate on your work.EquipmentThe building has fully equipped individual offices, team offices, coworking and conference rooms. The interior of the building meets the most modern office standards, fulfilling all the demands of the future-oriented working environment and offering employees a unique atmosphere.Location and accessibilityThe Agendis Business Center is located in a new business area at Frankfurt Airport. The surrounding area offers an excellent infrastructure with optimal transport connections as well as various shopping facilities. Are you looking for an office or flexible office space in a modern and luxurious style in Frankfurt? Please contact us for a viewing of this business center in Frankfurt.

Check out our 250 m2 of light flooded space in the heart of Kreuzberg 61, covered by only 12 enormous desks of 2 x 1 meter. 
Just 250,- € net a month for a desk We offer a stylish and inspiring environment for those who already know who they are and are seeking a place for concentrated work and a community that is hard to find.  We are around for more than five years and have build a social network of selected tenants from different professions such as designers, PR-specialists, 3D-artists, business consultants, programmers and social activists from all over the world. -2x1 m Eiermann Design table-high-end Italian office chair-lockable cabinet-VoIP telephone line with your own number-your company's name on all signs (gateway, external door, entrance) -your company's name on the mailbox-complementary coffee from "Barcomi's"-alcohol-free beverages and beer at a wholesale price-fully-equipped conference room with beamer, flip-chard, whiteboard and Eams-chairs-three separated and spacious telephone cabinets for longer talks / Skype-2 separate 60.000 WiFi nets24 / 7 access-Access to a big, fully-equipped kitchen
  We are looking forward meeting you!

Are you looking for an affordable and central coworking space in the popular state capital?
Our premises are located on the 11th floor of a modern office building directly on the Mittlerer Ring. Here you will find everything you need in an office: Instead of having to buy a desk with printer, copier and co. yourself, you can rent a fully equipped office with WLAN and telephone system and use the existing infrastructure.
Over the shared roof terrace, which invites you to rest and relax, you can enjoy a fantastic 360-degree view over Munich. Also our kicker offers the possibility to switch off and recharge your batteries. And if you want to get really worked up, you can use the company's own fitness room.
Our 360° tour will give you a first impression of the premises:
https://app.immoviewer.com/portal/tour/1167811?accessKey=5a88

The oldest preserved town house in Düsseldorf. Centrally located in Düsseldorf's old town on Heinrich-Heine-Allee. In the middle of the busy and well-known pedestrian zone 'Flinger Straße'. Within walking distance to the Japanese Quarter and the main station. Impressive by the interaction of the ancient facade from 1627 and the innovative, modern furnishing.
Here you are guaranteed to find the right space for your event. No matter whether seminars, meetings, conferences, workshops or conferences.
We have lovingly designed meeting rooms, conference rooms, conference and seminar rooms, innovation labs as well as special project offices on approximately 800 square meters.
Companies will find think tanks for corporate coworking, creative space for open innovation and a real alternative to the usual conference rooms, meeting rooms and seminar rooms in Düsseldorf.
And what Düsseldorf offers is right on the doorstep: the longest counter in the world. The extensive sunny bank of the Rhine. Great offers from gastronomy to culture.
Come with us on a tour and discover our rooms & prices. Convince yourself of the comprehensive equipment and the central location.

The A22 Coworking & Rooms are located in downtown Esslingen between Burg and Rathausplatz. Due to its central location, the building has excellent public transport connections. In the surrounding area there is a large gastronomic offer, as well as a multiplicity of shopping possibilities.The bright rooms convince by their modern equipment and offer space for lone fighters and teams. Benefit from monthly cancelable membership options and a comprehensive service.

This is a fantastic place to work: Not only is the historic Bauhaus loft a prominent and impressive setting, it is also easily accessible and convenient.
It benefits from high ceilings, big windows and a floor area of about 50 sq metres, and is flooded with natural light. This trendy and comfy co-working space makes the most of both design and function, easily enabling you to work creatively and efficiently as well as delighting your customers. They also offer more flexible pricing models including 1 day, 5 day, 12 day and 1 month tickets starting from €17.50.

Munich is one of the largest coworking cities in Germany. This coworking space is one of the small independent providers in the state capital. Thanks to its central location in Maxvorstadt, you can reach all important places in no time. It is also close to the university. Especially start-ups and freelancers are at home in this space. The local team uses most of the space as an open space area, but it is also possible to rent 3 offices. Community dinners offer regular opportunities to get to know the community better, the natural exchange is very important and offers the possibility to share ideas. Especially for the geographical location the price is indeed unbeatable.
 
Rental prices and equipment
The office equipment is perfectly designed for coworking space. Most of the workstations are located in open space. Here you can work at various table groups or use the three private offices of different sizes. The tables are individually manufactured by a small wood workshop in Bavaria. Therefore all things have high quality, practicality and modernity at the same time. Wooden telephone booths have been integrated for short-term calls. If you need a long break, you can also use one of the two conference rooms or retire to different armchairs throughout Space. As a member of the community you have a coffee and tea flat rate. This also applies to the use of printers and scanners. All Fix Desk tenants also have their own lockers and can use the conference room free of charge.
 
Location and accessibility
Travelling by car is certainly possible, but not always advisable due to limited parking space. Parking spaces can be rented in the surrounding multi-storey car parks for 150 euros. Arrival by public transport, however, is very easy. The university's subway station is only a few hundred meters away from Space, where the U3 and U6 stop. The tram lines 27 and 28 run along Schellingstraße. A bus stop (lines 153 and 154) is also within walking distance. Further away is the underground Theresienstraße or Josephplatz with the underground lines U2 and U8.

Your new flexible office is centrally located in the Neustadt with a unique view over the harbour and the Speicherstadt. This business centre focuses on customer needs and offers very high quality.

Rental prices and equipmentThe Business Center offers you flexible, fully equipped offices and coworking workstations. Here you will find a lot of design at an attractive price. A High Speed LAN and WIFI are already included in the price. Other additional costs such as cleaning and filtered water are also included. Meeting rooms are also at your disposal, for which you already have a monthly contingent for 4 persons included in the price. A meeting lounge is also available free of charge for office customers. You can find an individual office from € 390.00 and a team office from € 690.00. 

Location and accessibilityThe Business Center is located in the city center near the port of Hamburg. The Speicherstadt and HafenCity are not far from the property. Numerous shopping and gastronomic offers can be found in the immediate vicinity. The Baumwall underground station provides access to public transport. The connection to the A1 motorway (Hamburg-Süd triangle) is reached within 5 minutes by car via the Elbe bridges.

Arrange a viewing appointment right away.

Beehive's office space is centrally located in the Frankfurt train station district and is part of the Fintech Center. The office space has private offices and an open space with work and meeting rooms.Rental PricesThe office space offers space for up to 4 employees and can be rented here on short or long-term basis at flexible conditions. Our team will be happy to assist you in finding the optimal composition of your office space so that you can concentrate on your work.EquipmentThe modern offices are already fully equipped and meet all the requirements of the future working world. Arcade games and coffee specialities await you in the break area.Location and accessibilityThe Beehive Frankfurt at Mainzerlandstraße 33a is centrally located in the Frankfurt train station district. The surrounding area offers an optimal infrastructure as well as connections to the central station and public transport. Are you looking for an office or flexible office space in a modern style in the centre of Frankfurt? Please contact us for a viewing of this coworking space in Frankfurt.

Our Coworking Space in Kaiser-Wilhelm-Straße 83 is located in a beautiful Art Nouveau “Kontorhaus” in Hamburg city center, between Gänsemarkt, Johannes Brahms Platz and the park Planten & Blomen. Here you will find a creative feel-good atmosphere on two floors that follows the theme „beehive“. High ceilings and windows impart a creative loft character. The open space provides you with different work opportunities that allow for flexible use. Cozy rest areas with picnic table, arcade games and good coffee specialties invite you to a creative break. Here you will find everything you need. You can reach BEEHIVE Holstenhof within 5 walking minutes by underground U2 (Gänsemarkt). Directly in front of the entrance is the bus stop: Johannes-Brahms-Platz (Line: 3, 35, 607 ). Nearby is also one hire station of StadtRAD (Axel Springer Platz).

You will find the location in Hamburg-Bahrenfeld at Otto von Bahrenpark. This area is one of the most popular office locations in Bahrenfeld. The architecture of the area is characterised by historical and traditional red brick facades. The new buildings are consistently adapted to the historical stock. In the buildings and halls you will find hotels, restaurants, fitness clubs, supermarkets and shops for daily needs in addition to various office tenants.
Rental prices and equipment
The representative office areas are modernly equipped and offer a variety of work and meeting rooms. Both individual offices and team offices can be rented here flexibly. In addition to the private offices, coworking workstations can also be rented. The prices for the private offices start at EUR 257 per workstation and a coworking workstation is available from EUR 139.
Location and accessibility
The Otto von Bahrenpark is located in the middle of Bahrenfeld and you can find everything your heart desires. Here you will find numerous supply possibilities, which leave nothing to be desired. The connection by car as well as by public transport is very good.  There are numerous parking spaces on the site, and the connection to the A7 motorway is quickly reached via Bahrenfelder Chaussee. In addition to the "Bahrenfeld" suburban railway station, you can also reach the Altona long-distance train station on foot, where you will find other suburban railway and bus connections in addition to the long-distance trains.

Neukölln is our newest coworking space in Berlin, located in the iconic Geyer Werke building. With a mix of team rooms, coworking areas, event spaces, and creative studios, our house in Neukölln is about going back to our roots.
Offer & Rental Prices
In this building you rent stylish and fully equipped offices. Prices start at € 1.050,- per month, including the additional costs for a 3-person office.
Generous space with Berlin backyard charm
Rooms with more than 25 workstations and more are also available in various sizes on over 4.000m² and are located in separate wings or floors. In addition, there is a spacious courtyard, community and meeting rooms, free yoga classes and much more for all members.
Location & Surroundings
Neukölln is one of the most multicultural districts of Berlin. Bakeries and discounters can be found in the lively streets. The picturesque side streets with their second-hand stores, hip bars and cafés are popular with students and artists.
 
Interested ? Ask us now for your individual offer or book a tour right away.

Become part of a community in Berlin Kreuzberg of more than 500 entrepreneurs, start-ups, creators, movers and shakers, freelancers, early-stage technology start-ups, businesses, non-profit organizations, service providers, small businesses and remote teams of all kinds.
Rental Prices
In this building you rent stylish and fully equipped offices. Prices start at € 2.100,- per month, including the additional costs for a 6-person office.
Roof terrace, meeting rooms & community garden
Rooms with more than 25 workstations and more are also available in various sizes and are located in separate wings or floors. In addition, there is a roof terrace, a community garden, and community and meeting rooms for all members.
Location & surroundings
Kreuzberg is one of the most sought-after locations in Berlin. The subway "Checkpoint Charlie" is nearby, as well as parks, many cafes and restaurants.
 
Interested ? Ask us now for your individual offer or book a tour right away.
8 eingerichtete Arbeitsplätze in ebenerdigem Büro. Parkplätze und Bushaltestelle direkt vor dem Gebäude. Verkehrsgünstig in nächster Nähe Kreuzung B2/A8 gelegen.

Bei uns kann man in angenehmer und professioneller Umgebung mit sozialem Anschluss flexibel arbeiten. Monats-,Wochen-, oder auch nur Tageweise. Die Arbeitsplätze sind teilweise mit elektrisch höhenverstellbaren Tischen ausgestattet. Es sind derzeit am Standort Augsburg bis zu 25 Arbeitsplätze nutzbar. Miniküche mit Spüle, Wasser, Kühlschrank und Kochgelegenheit sind im Büro vorhanden. Ein modernes Betriebsrestaurant ist auf dem Gelände vorhanden und kann von jedem genutzt werden. Besprechungsräume und PKW-Parkplatz können bei Bedarf separat gebucht werden.

Inmitten eines attraktiven Büroviertels in Düsseldorf befindet sich das Business Center in der 9. Etage des Hochhauses THREE GEORGE mit einem hervorragenden Ausblick auf den Rhein. Stilvoll und exklusiv präsentiert es sich inmitten Unternehmen aus der Modebranche, Privatbanken und Beratungsunternehmen. Genießen Sie die äußerst geschmackvolle Einrichtung unseres Business Centers, die in Zusammenarbeit mit dem renommierten Innendesigner „Eric Kuster Metropolitan Living“ entworfen wurde.

Erhoben über der Düsseldorfer Innenstadt befindet sich unser zweites COLLECTION Business Center im landesweit bekannten Dreischeibenhaus. In diesem bedeutenden Landmark der Stadt Düsseldorf, welches erst kürzlich eine umfassende Revitalisierung erfahren hat, bieten wir Ihnen Büros in moderner Atmosphäre und einer noch nie da gewesenen Eleganz.
Das gemeinsam mit dem niederländischen Innendesigner ERIC KUSTER Metropolitan Luxury ausgearbeitete Konzept stellt eine neue Dimension in der Business Center Branche dar. Unsere eleganten Einzelbüros, Teambüros und Chefbüros sind komplett und stilvoll ausgestattet und können provisionsfrei und mit flexiblen Vertragslaufzeiten angemietet werden.

The COLLECTION Business Center Stuttgart-Königstraße is located in the city's most exclusive location, in the middle of the city and in the immediate vicinity of Schlossplatz, on the 6th floor of a newly built office building with sophisticated, modern architecture. Enjoy the view from our impressive roof terrace over the whole of Stuttgart and act at the pulse of the Swabian metropolis.
Look forward to modern, light-flooded and spacious offices of various sizes. What makes our COLLECTION Business Center unique in Stuttgart is the layout and ambience designed in partnership with the renowned interior designer Eric Kuster Metropolitan Living, which meets the highest demands.

Kurze Beschreibung:
Das collective.ruhr in Essen bietet seit September 2018 Coworking auf 800m² für Freiberufler und Mitarbeiter aus den verschiedensten Branchen. 
 
Die Idee hinter collective.ruhr ist es, ein Netzwerk aus Freiberuflern und Firmen sowie Kreativen aus der Region zu knüpfen und auf diese Weise eine lebendige und produktive Gemeinschaft aufzubauen. Neben dem gemeinsamen Arbeiten sind daher Konzerte aus der Reihe “Overtime Sessions” und Ausstellungen ein fester Bestandteil von collective.ruhr.
 
Besonderes Highlight: Die 60m² große Dachterrasse mit viel Platz zum Relaxen und Beisammensein in der Mittagspause und nach Feierabend.

Wie sieht es drinnen aus?
Ein durchdachter Mix aus offenen Arbeitsplätzen im Open Space sowie abgeschlossenen Büros und Meetingräumen sorgt bei collective.ruhr gemeinsam mit einer gemütlichen Lounge-Ecke für die perfekte Atmosphäre zum Arbeiten und Netzwerken. Auch die große Gemeinschaftsküche mit angrenzender Dachterrasse und BBQ-Grill lädt alle Mitglieder sowie Kunden, Freunde und Partner zum Verweilen und Kennenlernen ein.

Das Gebäude liefert alle Grundlagen für eine Sicherheitsstandard TISAX Level 3 / Prototypen - Zertifizierung.

In unmittelbarer Nähe zum Forschungs- und Innovationszentrum FIZ der BMW Group gelegen, bietet das Bürogebäude maximale Flexibilität.

 Die Arbeitswelt ist im Wandel. Wir unterstützen Sie beim Ankommen in der neuen Normalität – und machen Ihnen zu unserem 15-jährigen Firmenjubiläum ein besonderes Geschenk: Bei Vertragsunterzeichnung bis zum 31. Mit unserem flexiblen und skalierfähigen Flächenangebot inklusive verlässlichem Hygienekonzept machen Sie Arbeitsorte wieder gemeinsam erlebbar. Ein weiteres Highlight, gerade für Start-ups, sind die sechs hochmodernen Coworking Spaces. Sie können monatlich einen festen Platz anmieten oder tageweise flexibel einen freien Platz nutzen. Stilvolle Lounges und Teeküchen laden zum Verweilen, Kraft tanken und Netzwerken ein. Das Bürozentrum in der Maximilianstraße liegt an einer der vier „königlichen“ Straßen Münchens, die Mitte des 19. Jahrhunderts angelegt wurden. Die Straße und der Baustil der Gebäude wurden nach König Maximilian II. benannt, der englische Gotik und italienisches Design miteinander kombiniert hat. Das Geschäftszentrum liegt in der Nähe der wichtigen Regierungsgebäude, darunter das palastartige Maximilaneum am Ufer der Isar, dem Sitz des bayrischen Landtags, und des Hauptpostamts. Die wohlhabende Maximilianstraße ist bekannt für ihre exklusiven Geschäfte und Restaurants und liegt in Münchens kulturellem Viertel, in der Nähe des Theaters, der Oper und einigen der besten Hotels der Stadt. Es gibt ausgezeichnete Straßen- sowie öffentliche Verkehrsverbindungen und das Gebäude bietet eine sichere Tiefgarage.

Across the Ruhr region, there are industrial cities of the past that are being revitalised by modern growth and business. Oberhausen is the perfect example of this regrowth. In the new-build office space of this Regus location, you’ll find co-working spaces, meeting rooms and hot desks, all with high-speed Wi-Fi and modern furnishings. This business centre has everything to keep you productive and on track, including on-site parking and 24-hour access. The site borders one of the largest shopping malls in the area and means that everything from food to office supplies and electronics are a stone’s throw away.
You have great access to local transport with the Neue Mitte Bus and Light Rail Station 200 metres up the road. Want to take a break? Book a tour around the Peter-Behrens-Bau, a collection depot for the vast LVR-Industriemuseum. It’s part of a seven-building display on Germany’s industrial past, and a great place to inspire you to go above and beyond in your productivity. And around the corner is another industrial icon, the Gasometer. This former Gas tank now contains exhibits and art installations with incredible surrounding views. With these surroundings, it’s hard not to have a productive mindset whenever you work at Regus Oberhausen.

LANGLANG Coworking:small and yet so big LANGLANG Coworkingis a 50'square meter feet office, owner-operated coworking space in Berlin Moabit. How do I get to LangLang Coworking? The easiest way to get to Havelbergerstr. 5 is by underground U9 Birkenstrasse, which stops less than seven minutes from Space. For those who prefer to take the bus, the M27 is available. Get off at the stop U Reinickendorfer Str./Fennstr with U6. Here the way is about 4 stations long with bus. If you prefer to drive there by car, there are no parking spaces to worry about. There are sufficient possibilities to park in front of the Space. What's in the neighborhood? The neighbourhood invites to one or the other culinary journey. The Osmanya restaurant is a few hundred metres from Space and offers a new interpretation of classic turkish dishes. A little further away (about 5 minutes walk) you will find the vegan Valladares Feinkost or the Crunch Kantine. Here you can end the day in a relaxed atmosphere. But there are also inexpensive snack bars for small businesses. The prices - completely fair At LANGLANG, in addition to the coffee and tea flat rate, the Internet, electricity and the use of the multi-device for scanning, printing and copying are also included. You can get a Flex-Desk for one day for 15 Euro. The workplace is available during the opening hours from 9.00 - 18.00 o'clock and has once a week for one hour a tax and legal consultant. You get a fix desk for 180 Euro / month. If you just want to try it out for a day, you can do it for free. The prices are all inclusive of taxes.

Und falls Sie mal ins Zentrum von Düsseldorf wollen, nehmen Sie einfach einen Bus, der Sie in wenigen Minuten ins Stadtzentrum bringt. Düsseldorf genießt einen Ruf als Modestadt, daher beweist auch das Business Center an der Königsallee 106 echtes Stilgefühl. Sobald Sie das atemberaubende Gebäude mit Glasfront erblickt und den geräumigen Empfangsbereich betreten haben, werden Sie beeindruckt sein.

Das Geschäftszentrum an der Königsallee, Düsseldorf liegt in der Altstadt, in der vierten und fünften Etage einer der renommiertesten Geschäftsadressen Düsseldorfs. Düsseldorf gilt als "Paris von Deutschland" und ist die Heimat vieler bekannter Marken. Das Geschäftszentrum liegt an der langen Einkaufsstraße Königsallee, die als die Nabe der Modebranche des Landes gilt und in der weltweit führende Designer mehrmals im Jahr ihre Kollektionen vorstellen. Das benachbarte Bankenviertel liegt besonders im Fokus von Finanzdientleistern, Managementberatern und Steuerprüfern. Das Gebäude liegt in der Nähe vieler Restaurants, Banken und Einzelhandelsgeschäfte. Sie liegen nahe dem Rhein und nur wenige Gehminuten von Straßenbahn, Bus und U-Bahnhöfen entfernt.
Vom Standort Seestern im Prinzenpark aus erreichen Sie in nur 10 Minuten die Innenstadt. Bahnhof und Autobahn liegen nur wenige hundert Meter entfernt.

Mit seiner großflächigen Begrünung und fließenden Fassade aus weißem Stein und Glas liegen die Büroräume in einem architektonischen Meisterwerk mit gemischter Nutzung. Der Standort des Business-Centers ist ein Verkehrsknotenpunkt am Rande des Hofgartens und in der Nähe aller wichtigen Einrichtungen im Zentrum von Düsseldorf.

Die modernen und flexiblen Büroräume befinden sich in einer optimalen Stadtlage. Man kann den Düsseldorfer Hauptbahnhof in nur 5 Kilometer erreichen, sowie die Innenstadt. Wenige Meter entfernt befinden sich ein Fitness-Club, Hotels und Restaurants. Den Flughafen erreichen Sie in rund 7 Minuten.

Unsere neuen Büros in der Bismarckstraße in Mönchengladbach sind direkt in der Innenstadt Mönchengladbachs und nur wenige Meter von der für Einkäufe beliebten Hindenburgstraße, mit ihren Restaurants und Cafes, entfernt gelegen. Das Center erreicht man als Autofahrer in nur wenigen Minuten verkehrsgünstig von der Autobahn A 52 und es stehen kostenpflichtige Parkplätze zur Verfügung. n unmittelbarer Nähe zum Business Center findet sich zudem eine Bushaltestelle mit diversen Anbindungen in die Stadt sowie ins Umland und auch der Hauptbahnhof Mönchengladbach ist fussläufig erreichbar, was auch eine Anreise mit dem Zug einfach gestaltet. Diese neu renovierten Arbeitsplätze und Konferenzräume stehen Ihnen bei Bedarf zur Verfügung, und die Online-Buchung ist denkbar einfach.

Die Büroräume befinden sich an dem beeindruckenden neuen Standort Airport City direkt am Flughafen und warten mit hervorragenden Verkehrsanbindungen auf. Der Flughafen bietet neben internationalen Anbindungsmöglichkeiten auch erstklassige Straßen- und Bahnverbindungen – hier arbeiten Sie nur 10 Minuten von der Düsseldorfer Innenstadt entfernt.

Das Geschäftszentrum im Stadttor liegt auf der 17. Etage eines preisgekrönten Gebäudes im Medienhafen der Stadt. Das Medienhafen-Projekt hat es sich zum Ziel gesetzt, den Düsseldorfer Industriehafen in ein blühendes Kultur- und Medienviertel zu verwandeln. In dieser Stadt sind bereits 400 Werbeagenturen ansässig, darunter die drei größten in Deutschland.

Das Königsallee 61 Business Center überblickt die Königsallee in Düsseldorf, einen beeindruckenden baumgesäumten Boulevard mit Kanal. Die Büros auf der ersten Etage befinden sich in einem eleganten, modernen Gebäude mit eigener Sonnenterrasse und reizvoller Aussicht auf den Boulevard, nahe der Altstadt und einer erstklassigen Einkaufsstraße. Zudem steht Ihnen in der Nähe ein großes Angebot an gehobenen Annehmlichkeiten zur Verfügung. Das am Rhein gelegene und mit einer hervorragenden Verkehrsinfrastruktur gesegnete Düsseldorf ist bekannt als wichtiges Zentrum für Deutschlands Werbe- und Modeindustrie. Es beheimatet viele internationale Finanzinstitute und eine der größten Aktienbörsen des Landes. Vor kurzem hat sich die Stadt den Ruf als eines der Top-Telekommunikationszentren Deutschlands erworben.
Die Büroräume des Centers befinden sich am Rande des dynamischen Geschäftsviertels von Deutz.

The Colonius Carré is a strikingly modern office building with unique architecture and an inspiring setting. Sitting in the creative and vibrant neighbourhood of Ehrenfeld, within view of the iconic Colonius telecommunications tower, the artistic vibe of this area infuses every office, meeting room and desk of the centre. A quadrangle sits at the heart of the complex, inviting workers to sit and rest for a while in a peaceful green space in contrast to the buzzing city surroundings.
With high-speed Wi-Fi connections, plug-and-play desk spaces and accommodating administrative staff, your productivity is assured. The building has great local transport links – a few steps down the road, you’ll find the Liebigstrasse Bus Stop, which in turn will connect you to the Enrehfeld Gutenbergstrasse Train and Light Rail stations. And for drivers, the centre has its own convenient parking garage. The area, known as a centre of media and movie production in Cologne, is filled with ideal destinations for after-work entertainment, such as the Live Music Hall and Cinedom Movie Theater.

Das Kranhaus-Center befindet sich im Hafengebiet als eines der drei faszinierenden Bauwerke aus dem 21. Jahrhundert. Das Design soll an Hafenkräne erinnern, die einst entlang des Rheinufers zu finden waren.

In einem Gebäude mit fantastischer Aussicht auf den Rhein und die Kölner Skyline befindet sich das Business Center. Es ist in einem architektonisch atemberaubenden modernen Gebäude untergebracht, einem von drei in Köln am Fluss entlang platzierten Gebäuden, die wie Hafenkräne aussehen.
Das hochmoderne Center befindet sich in einem Wohn- und Bürokomplex in Top-Lage inmitten der Innenstadt mit gutem Ausblick auf das Viertel.

Das Business Center ist in der Neumarkt Galerie integriert, die zentral in der Innenstadt liegt. Viele Büros und eine Reihe von Geschäften befinden sich in der unmittelbaren Nachbarschaft. Das Center ist sehr vekehrsgünstig gelegen, da es nur wenige Gehminuten zur nächsten U-Bahnstation sowie 25 Fahrminuten zum Flughafen entfernt. Köln ist ein etablierter Standort für viele führende Unternehmen.
Der KölnTurm überblickt den einzigartigen MediaPark im Herzen des Komplexes und erhebt sich majestätisch über ihn.

Die Büroräume des Königstraße-Centers bieten eine Adresse mit großartigem Prestige in einem historischen Gebäude, das als Symbol von Stuttgarts Identität gilt. Es befindet sich auf der sechsten Etage im Königsbau – ein von König Wilhelm I in Auftrag gegebenes und von 1856 bis 1860 im spätklassizistischen Stil erbautes Gebäude. Heute ist es eine erfolgreiche Mischung aus Tradition und Moderne und beheimatet Büroräume im Herzen einer Stadt, die für ihre wirtschaftlichen Innovationen weltweit einen hohen Stellenwert genießt.

Die Büroräume liegen auf der berühmten Stuttgarter Königstraße, möglicherweise der längsten Fußgängerzone Deutschlands, die am Hauptplatz der Stadt vorbeiführt. Beheimatet sind die Büros im fünften Stock eines modernen Gebäudes und Sie genießen von einer privaten Terrasse einen atemberaubenden Blick auf Stuttgart sowie auf die umliegenden Hügel. Die Stuttgarter Büroräume haben eine Tiefgarage und sind 2 Minuten von den wichtigsten Bahnverbindungen und dem U-Bahnhof Schlossplatz, mit schnellen Verbindungen zum Flughafen, entfernt. Stuttgart gilt als die Wiege des Automobils und ist immer noch die Heimat großer Autohersteller. Es zieht auch Hightech-Industrien an und die Region registriert eine hohe Anzahl an Patenten und Designs. Stuttgarts Börse ist die zweigrößte in Deutschland und es gibt viele führende Geldinstitute in der Stadt.
Das markante Bürogebäude ist ein Teil des Wiederaufbaus von Köln nach dem Krieg. Es wurde kürzlich komplett renoviert, um die allerneusten Technologien zu integrieren.

Direkt an der Universitätsklinik gelegen, bietet Ihnen dieses Business Center eine exzellente Ausgangslage, um Ihr Unternehmen an diesen Standort zu verlagern. Die Hansestadt genießt ein hohes Ansehen in der Bevölkerung und ist flächenmäßig sogar die größte Stadt in Schleswig-Holstein.

Der Südwestpark ist ein exzellenter Standort für Unternehmen aus allen Branchen. Aufgrund der umfassenden Lage direkt an der Autobahn sowie des eigenen S-Bahnhofs direkt am Gelände haben sich bereits 230 Unternehmen mit mehr als 8.000 Beschäftigen niedergelassen.

Das Business Center in Nürnberg bietet Kunden eine der am günstigsten gelegenen Geschäftsadressen in der Stadt sowie eine Reihe erstklassiger Support-Leistungen. Es befindet sich in einem modernen Gebäude im Herzen des Geschäftsviertels, ist von Verwaltungsgebäuden und zahlreichen Restaurants und Geschäften umgeben. Das Bürozentrum befindet sich in der 3. Etage des Gebäudes und verfügt über 36 voll ausgestattete Büros und drei Konferenzräume mit Blick über die Altstadt. Als Kunde des Centers werden Sie von einem professionellen mehrsprachigen Team vor Ort unterstützt und genießen die Vorzüge des Hochgeschwindigkeits-Internetzugangs und des Videokonferenzstudios, welches Ihnen unnötige Reisen erspart. Mit Produkten wie Businessworld können Sie weltweit Regus-Center nutzen und so unterwegs produktiv bleiben. Das Konzept der Komplettbüros bietet Ihnen skalierbare Einrichtungen für wachsende Unternehmen, und bewahrt Ihnen Ihre Flexibilität und Kosteneffizienz.

Die Büroräume liegen in einer sehr zentralen Lage. Der qualitativ hochwertige Standort ist für Unternehmen jeder Größe geeignet. Durch die direkte Stadtlage sind jegliche Besorgungen schnell erledigt und jede Menge Restaurants gegeben. Der Kreativität und Freiheit sind in unserem Business Center keine Grenzen gesetzt!

Aufsehenerregendes Business Center mit toller Aussicht auf die Kaiserburg und den Flughafen, der sich in unmittelbarer Nähe befindet. Die direkte Flughafenlage bietet nahe gelegene Einkaufsmöglichkeiten, sowie einen Friseur. Das Business Center ist durch seine unbestechliche Lage für jedes Unternehmen in jeglicher Größe geeignet. Freiraum für Ideen und Flexibilität sind hier keine Fremdwörter.

Das Colonius Carré ist ein absolut modernes Bürogebäude mit einzigartiger Architektur in einer inspirierenden Umgebung. Ehrenfeld ist ein kreatives und lebhaftes Viertel. In der Nähe befinden sich zum Beispiel der berühmte Colonius-Fernsehturm, und das künstlerische Flair der Gegend ist in den Büros und Konferenz- und Tagungsräumen des Centers allgegenwärtig. Im Herzen des Bürokomplexes befindet sich ein Innenhof, der zum Entspannen inmitten einer ruhigen Grünfläche einlädt, die das geschäftige Treiben der Stadt vergessen macht. Mit High-Speed-WLAN-Verbindungen, Plug-and-Play-Bürobereichen und hilfsbereiten Mitarbeitern für administrative Aufgaben müssen Sie sich keine Sorgen um Ihre Produktivität machen. Das Gebäude hat eine hervorragende Anbindung an den Nahverkehr – nur wenige Schritte entfernt befindet sich die Bushaltestelle Liebigstraße, über die Sie zu den Bahnhöfen an der Gutenbergstraße gelangen. Autofahrer können das Center-eigene Parkhaus nutzen. Dieses Kölner Viertel ist für seine Medien- und Filmproduktionsstandorte bekannt und wartet mit zahlreichen Unterhaltungsmöglichkeiten für den Feierabend auf. Zum Beispiel sind die Live Music Hall und das Cinedom-Kino ganz in der Nähe.

Find your perfect working environment on over 3,000 m². The innovative coworking space in the Westendgate Tower, overlooking Frankfurt, offers freelancers and companies ideal conditions for expanding business and celebrating business success. Whether you are looking for a separate office or a workstation in the coworking space, the modern and coherent interior will certainly convince you to set up your tent here.
Rental Prices
Here you can rent coworking spaces or a private office for short or long periods at flexible contractual conditions. The local community managers will also ensure that you feel comfortable in this building and that your workplace is exactly what you want. The rental price includes various networking events, coffee and tea specialties and regular cleaning. The offices offer space for 4 to 200 people, even a short-term increase or reduction in size can be quickly realised thanks to the flexible rental period.
Facilities
The location in the Westendgate Tower in Frankfurt offers generous office space in various sizes in addition to workstations in the coworking space. To increase productivity, members have access to a fast and secure Internet connection, modern conference rooms with multimedia systems, kitchens with coffee bars and lounges where the community can network in a comfortable atmosphere.
Location and accessibility
The Business Center is located in Frankfurt's Westend district, opposite the main entrance to the Frankfurt Trade Fair. The connection to the public transport network is very good, which means you can reach Frankfurt's main railway station directly. The surrounding multi-storey car parks also offer sufficient parking facilities within a short distance. The A648, A66 and A5 motorways are only a few minutes away.

This rent24 in Berlin-Mitte on Oberwallstraße has 7200 m² of inspiring office, coworking and event space. The modern furnished offices and workstations offer the members an inspiring and productive working atmosphere. In addition to the possibility to productively advance your business, the spacious areas also offer space for relaxation and interesting exchange with other members. Start-ups as well as international companies have found their perfect space here.
Rental price
A single workstation can be rented for at least one month from 150 €/month on a flexible basis for short or long periods. A fixed workplace is available from 325 €/month, whereas a private office can be rented from 585 €/month. All memberships include free W-LAN, scanner and printer use, coffee, water and cleaning. Furthermore, the lounge can be used around the clock.
Location and accessibility
The optimal transport connection is a further plus point for this space. Located directly at the Hausvogteiplatz subway station, you can reach your new office in a few minutes on foot with the U2 subway or bus line 147, Werdescher Straße stop. The surrounding parking garages also make it possible to arrive by car or motorcycle.
Let yourself be inspired by these creative spaces, benefit from networking events or simply take a breath of fresh air while playing table tennis, table football or at the PlayStation.
We are happy to advise you.

In the historic building from 1930, which was extensively renovated, you will find this modern and stylish coworking space on 2 floors and a total of 1,500 sqm. Besides this location, Rent24 also operates a second location in Schöneberg, which is only a few house numbers away.
Rental prices/equipment
The Coworking Space has 157 coworking workstations and 14 private offices that can be rented flexibly. In addition to the workstations, there are also 4 meeting rooms that you can book if required and an event space where networking events are regularly held. If you want to relax actively in between, you will find a large area with a foosball table and a table tennis table, there is also a Playstation here. For a quieter rest you can also use the library and relax by reading a book. If you have a dear dog that you would like to take with you, then this is also no problem here. You can find a flexible workplace from EUR 175,00/month, a fix desk from EUR 300,00/month and a private office for 3 people from EUR 1.200,00/month. The prices already include utilities, cleaning, internet, coffee/tea, water and even fruit.

Location and accessibilityIn the surrounding area of this location you will find various restaurants, bars and cafés. You can easily reach this location by public transport via the bus stop in front of the building, or via the underground station Kleistpark and the subway station Yorckstraße. The city motorway can be reached within a few minutes and the Berlin main station is also only a 10 minute drive away.

This coworking space is located at Potsdamer Strasse 188 in Berlin. The provider is a real size and has several locations in Germany and abroad and sets new standards for flexible offices and coworking. The facility offers a healthy combination of work and leisure. Open and representative common areas are complemented by attractive work areas. Here, too, the community is at the centre of attention and networking, communication and cooperation are the basic elements of the modern working environment. However, if you prefer to have your peace and quiet, this is also possible.
 
Rental prices & equipment
The price for a Flex Desk is 175 Euro per month and for a private office, which can also be rented flexibly, you pay about 1200 Euro - depending on the size of the office and the agreed rental period. The different offices offer space for 3 to 15 people, furthermore there is also the possibility to realize your individual office for more than 15 employees. In the common areas there is a foosball table as well as a table tennis table and a playstation for a short break. In addition, many lounges and seating areas invite you to linger. Here is an opportunity to take a break again and again or to become creative.
 
Location & Accessibility
In terms of the physical, Potsdamer Straße offers a culinary diversity that is second to none. In addition to numerous fast-food restaurants, you will also find exquisite Italian specialties in walking distance. For those who like Mexican cuisine, we recommend the restaurant Zapata. You should definitely try the Burritos Mixtas. The building is located very close to the subway station Kleistpark, where the U7 stops. In addition, bus lines 106, 187, 204, M48, M85 and N7 also stop there. This offers you the best arrival and departure possibilities with public transport. If you like to travel by car, you should be prepared for the typical parking problems in Berlin.
 
Please contact us if you have any questions or would like to visit us.

The coworking space is located in the heart of Berlin's east directly at Prenzlauer Berg on 7,700 sqm and over 8 floors. The location offers space for a total of 647 coworking workstations, 200 private offices and 19 meeting rooms. Weekly events take place here, which offer many networking opportunities.
Rental fees/equipmentThe offices and workstations are fully equipped and the entire building has a fast WIFI. Offices are available in various sizes, both small offices and large offices can be rented flexibly. The areas are stylishly designed overall. Costs such as electricity, running costs, cleaning, internet and also coffee/tea, water and fruit are already included in the price. The lounges and kitchens are available for all members. Meeting rooms can also be booked by the hour if required. A private office is available from EUR 2.300,00 for a 4-person office.

Location and accessibilityThe location is in Berlin Mitte and is surrounded by various restaurants, bars and cafés. Shopping facilities are also in the immediate vicinity. Public transport connections are provided by the trams "M" and "M8" as well as the "Alexanderplatz" station, which is only 500m away and where you will find numerous S-Bahn and U-Bahn connections. You will find parking spaces for your car in the nearby multi-storey car park at Alexanderplatz, where you can also rent permanent parking spaces.

The ultra-modern offices at Friedrichstrasse 200 in Berlin Mitte were developed by one of the leading German insurance companies. Knowledge centers for the digital transformation of the insurance industry have been created. Join a community of freelancers and start-ups, collaborate with insurance experts and get advice on your business challenges in seconds. We offer you intelligent room concepts, high-quality equipment and designs that convey openness and creativity. All rooms are tastefully furnished and fully functional. And because it's located in the center of Philip Johnson House, it's also easy to reach the shared offices. The post-modern building is crowned by an oversized pop art sculpture that can be admired in the vestibule.
 
Rental Prices & Facilities
Individual desks for freelancers or start-ups can be rented, as well as small offices for 2-4 people and large team offices or project offices, you can decide whether they should be furnished or unfurnished. A fast internet connection is guaranteed by the fibre optic connection in the house. Further included in the rental prices are amenities like: Balcony, roof terrace, parking spaces in the courtyard and in the underground car park, 24/7 access, printer, networking events and cold drinks. Please contact us and we will negotiate the best price for you.
 
Location & Accessibility
Shopping after work is easy as there are many supermarkets, bakeries, restaurants and cafes nearby as well as many business lunches and dinners. Impressive historical sights and government offices are just a few meters from the office. The nearby subway stations Checkpoint Charlie (U6) and Stadtmitte (U2, U6) provide the fastest route to your new office.

The new rent24 coworking and event space is situated in the middle of Dortmunds city center.
On 1500 square meters rent24 offers convenient business and workplace solutions in a central and creative surrounding with weekly networking events and common areas for members.
The use of the lounges and activity rooms can enable you to create new contacts or just take a break from a stressful workday!
Thanks to the central location of the space there are great restaurants and bars right around the corner giving you lots of options for lunches or an after-work-drink!

The brand new rent24 coworking and event space is located in the middle of Bremen’s historical city center.
With 1050 square meters rent24 offers modern coworking and event spaces with activity and community areas.
A perfect environment for all types of professionals and entrepreneurs. This is a great central location and is surrounded by a wide variety of restaurants, bars and shops.
Take full advantage of the benefits provided such as an inspiring working atmosphere, network possibilities, a young and innovative community and weekly events. Come together at the activity areas that are equipped with table tennis, table soccer, PlayStation and much more.
Join the rent24 community in their brand new Bremen space today!

This coworking space in the heart of the city center is the perfect meeting place for Bremen's digital and startup scene. At 1,050 square meters, with open coworking areas, individual offices and community areas invite you to work and meet productive people. Become part of the rent24 community in Bremen.

Opposite the Elbphilharmonie Concert Hall, in the beautiful HafenCity you will find the location and your new flexible office or coworking workplace. Networking events also take place here regularly, where you can get to know the other office users even better and expand your network. 
Rental fees/equipment
The offices and community areas are designed in a rustic loftstyle and are available for short-term rent. Depending on your needs, you can rent offices in various sizes, either short-term or long-term, or you can opt for a coworking workplace. The offices and coworking workstations are fully equipped. A fast internet connection is included as well as office cleaning. If required, you can also book meeting rooms.
Location and accessibilityThe location is opposite the Elbphilharmonie Concert Hall and thus directly on the Elbe. Numerous restaurants and cafés are located in the immediate vicinity. The city centre is within walking distance, where you will also find various shopping facilities. You can reach the location by public transport via the underground station "Baumwall". Car parking spaces can be rented in the underground car park.

On the famous Kurfürstendamm, the Berlin start-up scene has one of the largest and most innovative areas with flexible offices in the city at its disposal. With a total area of approx. 9,500 square metres, this space offers modern and highly flexible office space in a highly innovative atmosphere. The open and spacious public areas are connected with private offices and desks in the open space. This Space sees itself as a place where creativity and work come together.
Rental Prices & Equipment
The modern furniture harmonises with warm colours and creates a very special working environment. Everything looks high quality and durable, giving each area of the entire surface a clear structure. Light, colour, decoration and furniture form a comfortable unit. This gives the room a very warm feeling. You feel at home in your living space, but everything else is designed for a successful working day. All workplaces are furnished and convince with ergonomic furniture. They offer you the comfort you need for your work. Here you can also feel the love for detail and the main goal of creating a well-structured workplace.
 
Location & Accessibility
Numerous restaurants, cafés and shops are located near the office. These ensure that your lunch break and leisure time will not be boring and that business appointments are always a success. Thanks to the central location of WorkRepublic Berlin Kurfürstendamm you can arrive and depart carefree. Both the S-Bahn and the U-Bahn stop nearby. The underground station Kurfürstendamm is only a few hundred meters away, where the underground lines U1 and U9 run. The S-Bahn station Zoologischer Garten is also within walking distance.
 
Please contact us if you have any further questions.

You will find the location in the traditional merchant's house, which was built in 1905 and given a modern design in 2007. Here you will find private offices, lounge areas, coworking and event space on a total of 2,000 sqm, which makes it a high-quality working location.

Surrounded by the Binnenalster, a diverse shopping experience and an extensive culinary offering, this office provides a productive working environment. Ruby Hans Workspace is located in the city centre and is in the middle of the Fleet. Flexibility is essential here and there is a suitable offer for all needs. Rental prices and facilitiesIn addition to fully equipped high-quality offices with various inclusive services, you also have the option of renting coworking workstations flexibly. The best address in the city combined with a real estate treasure. In the historic Girardet Haus am Kö-Graben is our 5-star office, extensively expanded in 2020. True to our line of success, this architectural jewel from the early 20th century fits wonderfully into our portfolio. Around 100 years ago, the unique arcades were built on Königsallee, which are still considered a trademark of monumental architecture today.
